        "Nursing / healthcare licensure": "看護 / 医療資格認定",
        "Nursing education, licensure, endorsement, temporary permits, and compact license rules are handled by state boards of nursing and may differ by state.": "看護教育、資格認定、推薦(endorsement)、暫定許可、コンパクト資格の規則は州の看護委員会が扱い、州によって異なる場合があります。",
